headline: Abbott's Latest-Generation FreeStyle Libre 3 Plus Glucose Sensor Technology Launches in Canada
summary: Abbott (NYSE: ABT) today announced that its latest generation of sensor-based glucose monitoring technology, the FreeStyle Libre 3 Plus* sensor, is now available to Canadians living with diabetes. This innovative product features the world's smallest1,2 glucose sensor.
